  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a libgweather</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libgweather</application> package is a library used to
access weather information from online services for numerous locations.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (HTTP): <ulink url="&libgweather-download-http;"/>
